headline: JP Morgan Raises Target Price on Citi (C), Keeps Overweight Call
summary: Citigroup Inc. (NYSE:C) is one of the 10 Best Bank Stocks to Buy in 2026. On February 9, JPMorgan raised its target price on Citi by 3.1% to $134 (from $130), reiterating its Overweight rating on the stock.
